Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Avoid ast.Str on Python 3.8+
X-Developer-Signature: v=1; a=openpgp-sha256; l=1029; i=xtexchooser@duck.com;
 h=from:subject; bh=9mpKf0Za2Ale23TCSOLOTI2MYM1+7ovfkgyTUzpdy2c=;
 b=owGbwMvMwCW2U4Ij7wZL9ETG02pJDBni1usYp906eTStOiQpeY/5ZbnbR63yJYNSdwXoOd+4H
 F6965pNRykLgxgXg6yYIkuRYYM3q046v+iyclmYOaxMIEMYuDgFYCJt3xgZnl9+o7xwx4Nbedf+
 8P96w733Erd5c9XcWz+9SzJ4j8g7XGH479+Tq1H+qEGkcVbfS+FID5Wpy54eyftlwFAkKXmdO/E
 IGwA=
X-Developer-Key: i=xtexchooser@duck.com; a=openpgp;
 fpr=7231804B052C670F15A6771DB918086ED8045B91

It has been deprecated since Python 3.8 and was removed from Python 3.14+.

Link: https://github.com/html5lib/html5lib-python/pull/583
Signed-off-by: xtex <xtex@aosc.io>
---
 setup.py | 5 +++--
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/setup.py b/setup.py
index 30ee05758ae1..62272c188eeb 100644
--- a/setup.py
+++ b/setup.py
@@ -93,8 +93,9 @@ with open(join(here, "html5lib", "__init__.py"), "rb") as init_file:
         if (len(a.targets) == 1 and
                 isinstance(a.targets[0], ast.Name) and
                 a.targets[0].id == "__version__" and
-                isinstance(a.value, ast.Str)):
-            version = a.value.s
+                ((sys.version_info >= (3, 8) and isinstance(a.value, ast.Constant)) or
+                    isinstance(a.value, ast.Str))):
+            version = a.value.value if sys.version_info >= (3, 8) else a.value.s
 
 setup(name='html5lib',
       version=version,

